              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/39089384/" class="">水性善下，道贵谦卑</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/sahaja/" class=" " title="公益霎哈嘉瑜伽">公益霎哈嘉瑜伽</a>
                (霎哈嘉瑜伽微信服务号:sahajasz.)
              
